data.description: This adorable farmhouse charmer has all the beauty of the country, with modern updates and located just minutes from schools! Perched on an acre of picturesque land, with towering trees swaying on the breeze, this little piece of paradise has been made completely ready for its next owner. Natural light floods in the oversize bay window in the living area, and dances off rustic laminate flooring. A cedar focal wall presents a wood-burning stove to keep you toasty all winter. Neutral painted cabinets in the kitchen showcase stainless steel appliances and room for a large table. Master bedroom contains a large walk-in closet. 2 convenient baths have been updated: one with a mod corner shower has recently been taken down to the studs and completely remodeled. GORGEOUS! 2 additional good-sized bedrooms and a large mudroom/storage area round out the floor plan. Out back, streamlined solar panels save hundreds in utilities each year! An above-ground pool with custom deck will keep your crew entertained all summer. Storm shelter ensures your safety in well-known Missouri wild weather. Fabulous water feature can host koi, ducks and so much more. And, as if all this wasn't enough, a fenced and cross-fenced pasture out back will home your livestock ... bring your horses, goats, cattle ... and become one step closer to completely self-sustaining! You don't want to miss out on this one; once it's gone, it's gone! See it today!
